      <p>Full replacement means coordinating plumbers, tile crews, and waste hauling—often over several weeks. <a href="/bathtub-refinishing/">Bathtub refinishing</a> and <a href="/ceramic-tile-refinishing/">tile refinishing</a> give you a like-new appearance in days, not weeks.</p>
