      <h2>Best timing for make-ready projects</h2>
      <p>Refinishing is ideal right after move-out, before cleaning and painting. That way, any light dust from the project can be cleaned up once, and the new finish has time to cure before the next tenant moves in.</p>
      <p>Most tub and tile projects in rentals are completed in 1&ndash;2 days with 24&ndash;48 hours of cure time.</p>
    </div>

