      <ul>
        <li>Yellowed or stained tubs that are structurally sound.</li>
        <li>Outdated tile colors that make units harder to lease.</li>
        <li>Vanity tops that are otherwise solid but visually tired.</li>
        <li>Small chips and cracks that can be handled with <a href="/chip-and-crack-repair/">professional repair</a>.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>If the fixture is cracked through, leaking, or moving when stepped on, replacement may be safer. We will always give you an honest recommendation.</p>
